  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WORLD CREATION</h2>Create beautiful worlds with simple clicks, from giant windmills to snowy castles and add animals,humans and birds for an amazing creative experience.<br>Add blocks,animated props,trees, buildings and animals with different weather and lighting conditions easily.Change colors of blocks, add animated props and watch as your world comes alive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/531930c0345f6e86d96a4236d83364d6.poster.avif?t=1646226379\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/531930c0345f6e86d96a4236d83364d6.webm?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/531930c0345f6e86d96a4236d83364d6.mp4?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WALK MODE</h2>\"Walk\" Mode lets you create a character and walk around the world ,with the ability to customize your character with different costumes and colors.<br>Library lets you discover creations from around the world, with thousands of downloadable worlds and creations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/48a82fae1e7cc71c110bea3622db1f58.poster.avif?t=1646226379\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/48a82fae1e7cc71c110bea3622db1f58.webm?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/48a82fae1e7cc71c110bea3622db1f58.mp4?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHARE CREATIONS</h2>A super fun toy with a surprising amount of depth. No goals, no distractions, just a beautiful visual and audio experience with tons creative potential. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/b7d5e5a0ca8bf9495674e1686d328c34.avif?t=1646226379\" width=620 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD ANYTHING</h2>The ultimate sandbox experience for kids and adults alike, with relaxing gameplay and millions of possibilities.<br>You can also export your creations as .txt files, and import them as well.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WORLD CREATION</h2>Create beautiful worlds with simple clicks, from giant windmills to snowy castles and add animals,humans and birds for an amazing creative experience.<br>Add blocks,animated props,trees, buildings and animals with different weather and lighting conditions easily.Change colors of blocks, add animated props and watch as your world comes alive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/531930c0345f6e86d96a4236d83364d6.poster.avif?t=1646226379\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/531930c0345f6e86d96a4236d83364d6.webm?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/531930c0345f6e86d96a4236d83364d6.mp4?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WALK MODE</h2>\"Walk\" Mode lets you create a character and walk around the world ,with the ability to customize your character with different costumes and colors.<br>Library lets you discover creations from around the world, with thousands of downloadable worlds and creations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/48a82fae1e7cc71c110bea3622db1f58.poster.avif?t=1646226379\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/48a82fae1e7cc71c110bea3622db1f58.webm?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/48a82fae1e7cc71c110bea3622db1f58.mp4?t=1646226379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHARE CREATIONS</h2>A super fun toy with a surprising amount of depth. No goals, no distractions, just a beautiful visual and audio experience with tons creative potential. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763600/extras/b7d5e5a0ca8bf9495674e1686d328c34.avif?t=1646226379\" width=620 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD ANYTHING</h2>The ultimate sandbox experience for kids and adults alike, with relaxing gameplay and millions of possibilities.<br>You can also export your creations as .txt files, and import them as well.",
